## Overview
This report documents an interactive Tableau dashboard built from DePaul University's cleaned applicant intake dataset. The dashboard investigates which course is a popular anomaly in the US in comparison to India? The analysis found that: Full-time MBA appears in the top five preferred courses in the USA, but neither in India's top 5 nor in the top 10 general course intake preferences. The tools used for the data cleaning and analysis are python and google colab and tableau which was used for creating a dashboard and also story telling. This finding would mostly be used by the marketing department and admission teams.
